A4.text: The Astros won the World Series in 2022.

A5.text: The 2017 World Series was the championship series of Major League Baseball's (MLB) 2017 season. The Astros defeated the Dodgers, four games to three, to win their first World Series in franchise history, also becoming the first team from Texas to do so.

A6.text: They would further lose the 2019 World Series against the Washington Nationals and the 2021 World Series against the Atlanta Braves before winning their second World Series in 2022 against the Philadelphia Phillies.
